<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Confederacy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Confederacy,</orth> league, alliance, conspiracy: <cit><quote>she is one of this c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.192" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 192</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>heard of our c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.4.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 4, 38</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>under the countenance and c. of Lady Eleanor,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.1.168" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 1, 168</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a full-charged c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 2, 3</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>what c. have you with the traitors?</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 3.7.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 7, 44</bibl></cit>.
